Package: pigeonscraper
Type: Package
Title: Scrapes and shares race data from the American Racing Pigeons Union Website
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Tiago", "CabaÃ§o", email = "tiago.joao.cabaco@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Package that implements functions to scrape racing data from ARPU 
    website. It is build around the functionality of RSelelinum API to 
    interactevely scrape every race table stored on the National Race Datababse. 
    The output are two pre-processed and curated data sets.  
